CatDescriptText: Cutline for image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1960, pg. 19, reads: "Congratulations! - Fifth Ward Constable Tommy Smith, right, congratulated Josephine Jackson and Emily Neal of the First District, Fifth Ward Satellite [sic] Softball Team for its success in the city wide Women's Softball League competition. The Satellites rest in second place in the league standings.  O. T. Whiting, committeeman in the First District and sponsor of the team, looks on admiringly. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Satilites softball team players Josephine Jackson and Emily Neal, with First District Committeeman and team sponsor O. T. Whiting, and Fifth Ward Constable Tommy Smith, on playing field
